    {
        "url": "/quotes/athol_fugard_585595",
        "quote": "What I quickly discovered is that our so-called new South Africa has as much material for a story-teller as the old one. The landscape hasn't really changed. Who is in power now is different to who was in power then, but the squatter camps grow like cancer, the rich get richer, the poor get poorer.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Athol Fugard",
            "url": "/quotes/athol_fugard_585595"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Discovered",
                "url": "/topics/discovered"
