                "name": "South",
                "url": "/topics/south"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/athol_fugard_585596",
        "quote": "The reason I'm in San Diego is not because I want distance from South Africa but because I want proximity to the people I love. But I don't envy growing up in America. As ugly as aspects of it were, my biggest blessing was to be born a South African.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Athol Fugard",
            "url": "/quotes/athol_fugard_585596"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Love",
                "url": "/topics/love"
