    {
        "url": "/quotes/athol_fugard_585569",
        "quote": "'Master Harold' is about me as a little boy, and my father, who was an alcoholic. There's a thread running down the Fugard line of alcoholism. Thankfully I haven't passed it on to my child, a wonderful daughter who's stone-cold sober. But I had the tendency from my father, just as he had had it from his father.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Athol Fugard",
            "url": "/quotes/athol_fugard_585569"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
