    {
        "url": "/quotes/athol_fugard_585564",
        "quote": "From early on there were two things that filled my life - music and storytelling, both of them provoked by my father. He was a jazz pianist and also a very good storyteller, an avid reader. He passed both those interests on to me.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Athol Fugard",
            "url": "/quotes/athol_fugard_585564"
