    {
        "url": "/quotes/athol_fugard_585573",
        "quote": "In South Africa, success never presented the problems that it presents in New York. In New York, if you happen to be the flavor of the month, a lot of nonsense comes with it into your life.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Athol Fugard",
            "url": "/quotes/athol_fugard_585573"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "New",
