                "url": "/topics/south_africa"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/athol_fugard_585574",
        "quote": "A very close friend of mine keeps reminding me that since about the age of 50, I've been saying, 'I'm finished. I haven't got another one in me.' But somehow you do.",
